{"word":"H2976 - יָאַשׁ - yâʼash - yaw-ash' - Despair","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יָאַשׁ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>yâʼash"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>yaw-ash'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Despair"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விருதா, கூடாத நம்பிக்கையற்றுபோ, நம்பிக்கையற்றவன், ஆசையை விட்டுவிடு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1) to despair"},{"paragraph":"a) (Niphal) to be despaired, to be desperate"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel) to cause to despair"},{"paragraph":"as an interjection:"},{"paragraph":"2) It is hopeless!"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>desist</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>despond: - </i>(cause to) despair, one that is desperate, be no hope."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2976 - יָאַשׁ - yâʼash - yaw-ash'/2976\">H2976</a>, <a href=\"#/H2979 - יְאָתְרַי - yᵉʼâthᵉray - yeh-aw-ther-ah'ee/2979\">H2979</a>"}]}